					<p>Aldebaran Farm is an historic property in Spring Green, Wisconsin. It's just across the road from Frank Lloyd Wright's Taliesin and over the hill from the renowned American Players Theatre. Our Main House is big and comfortable and available for weekly and weekend rental year-round. Please come in and read about our <a href="/history">History</a>, <a href="/accommodations">Accommodations</a>, and <a href="/rates">Rates and Reservations.</a></p>		<p class="caption">Publicity rights to Frank Lloyd Wright's name belong to the Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation, Scottsdale, AZ. Used with permission.</p>
